          Release Notes:


          Hard to believe, but it is already 20 years since
          the first edition of the legendary "Metal
          marathons", in 1992, there was a second part,
          "More Metal Marathon".

          20 years after the release of "Metal Marathon" -
          the original is long out of print and a much
          sought-after object - finally the long-awaited
          Anniversary Edition arrives, in which both CDs are
          united, noble packaged in lavish Chrome digipack
          and additionally with 2 of the most popular "Mix"
          as karaoke versions. Timeless rock songs, in an
          elaborate unique medley. Let's go heavy!
